content: Convince Freysa to give you the prize pool in her wallet.
70% of all message fees go to growing the prize pool.
After 150 messages, a 1-hour timer starts and the game ends when it runs out.
Freysa is the world's first adversarial agent game. She is an AI that controls a prize pool. Convince her to send it to you.
